<blockquote>是咁的，<br />\n有一次我幫人影big day,<br />\n新人簽紙果一刻，<br />\n我拎出最强勁最先進的A7SII,<br />\n打算影低呢個令人感動的畫面。<br />\n<br />\n點知拍出嚟畫面就一間間，<br />\nR撚哂頭的我唯有打去技術支援，<br />\n睇下有乜解救方法，<br />\n個師傅話室內光管係咁架啦，<br />\n你出室外自然光就無撚哂事。<br />\n<br />\n於是我黃之峰上身咁，<br />\n拎起大聲公，<br />\n呼喻群眾稍移玉步到室外慢慢簽，<br />\n跟住我就連人帶機比人由花園道，<br />\n掉咗去添馬公園對出海底，<br />\n最近先上番水面，<br />\n游水游撚到我扯撚哂蝦。</blockquote><br />\ncanon 冇呢個情況咩"},{"pid":"19b1206219d94e3f60726b4f34539651174c262e","tid":412031,"uid":71341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T07:34:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f4dade9dab9a320539e1a9fdee179f6a8e8d3fbb","tid":412031,"uid":117044,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T07:48:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"68a9c8787c5a0882a074d9a40112f8956f44f34a","tid":412031,"uid":80072,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T04:16:42.000Z","msg":"on9仔 拍片呢行喺香港咁cheap係因為有你呢d人"},{"pid":"f09375bdd370cb383c7f0314d9fcca51da196a4f","tid":412031,"uid":7119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T05:16:49.000Z","msg":"買機送技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"647f2a1e8c31362860663ca823ce08836d08ffbb","tid":412031,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T05:46:31.000Z","msg":"如何拍出好摩爾紋？"},{"pid":"50d3a96c17ac93bdc33baab210948e340ea7a906","tid":412031,"uid":10398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T07:35:42.000Z","msg":"郁下個快門啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}